#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.dolphin.appdata.xml:10
msgid "Dolphin"
msgstr "Dolphin"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.dolphin.appdata.xml:11
msgid "Manage your files"
msgstr "Bainistigh do chuid comhad"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.dolphin.appdata.xml:13
msgid ""
"Dolphin is KDE's file manager that lets you navigate and browse the contents "
"of your hard drives, USB sticks, SD cards, and more. Creating, moving, or "
"deleting files and folders is simple and fast."
msgstr ""
"Is é Dolphin bainisteoir comhad KDE a ligeann duit nascleanúint a dhéanamh "
"agus brabhsáil a dhéanamh ar ábhar do thiomántán crua, do mhaidí USB, do "
"chártaí SD, agus níos mó. Is simplí agus tapa comhaid agus fillteáin a "
"chruthú, a bhogadh nó a scriosadh."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.dolphin.appdata.xml:14
msgid ""
"Dolphin contains plenty of productivity features that will save you time. "
"The multiple tabs and split view features allow navigating multiple folders "
"at the same time, and you can easily drag and drop files between views to "
"move or copy them. Dolphin's right-click menu provides with many quick "
"actions that let you compress, share, and duplicate files, among many other "
"things. You can also add your own custom actions."
msgstr ""
"Tá neart gnéithe táirgiúlachta i nDolphin a shábhálfaidh am duit. Ligeann na "
"cluaisíní iolracha agus na gnéithe radhairc scoilte duit nascleanúint a "
"dhéanamh ar fhillteáin iolracha ag an am céanna, agus is féidir leat comhaid "
"a tharraingt agus a scaoileadh go héasca idir radhairc chun iad a bhogadh nó "
"a chóipeáil. Soláthraíonn roghchlár deaschliceáil Dolphin go leor "
"gníomhartha tapa a ligeann duit comhaid a chomhbhrú, a roinnt agus a "
"dhúbailt, i measc go leor rudaí eile. Is féidir leat do ghníomhartha "
"saincheaptha féin a chur leis freisin."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.dolphin.appdata.xml:15
msgid ""
"Dolphin is very lightweight, but at the same time, you can adapt it to your "
"specific needs. This means that you can carry out your file management "
"exactly the way you want to. Dolphin supports three different view modes: a "
"classic grid view of all the files, a more detailed view, and a tree view. "
"You can also configure most of Dolphin's behavior."
msgstr ""
"Tá Dolphin an-éadrom, ach ag an am céanna, is féidir leat é a oiriúnú do do "
"riachtanais shonracha. Ciallaíonn sé seo gur féidir leat do bhainistíocht "
"comhad a dhéanamh díreach mar is mian leat. Tacaíonn Dolphin le trí mhodh "
"radhairc éagsúla: radharc eangaí clasaiceach de na comhaid go léir, radharc "
"níos mionsonraithe, agus radharc crainn. Is féidir leat an chuid is mó "
"d'iompar Dolphin a chumrú freisin."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.dolphin.appdata.xml:16
msgid ""
"Dolphin can display files and folders from many Internet cloud services and "
"other remote machines as if they were right there on your desktop."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir le Dolphin comhaid agus fillteáin ó go leor seirbhísí scamall "
"Idirlín agus meaisíní iargúlta eile a thaispeáint amhail is dá mba rud é go "
"raibh siad ansin ar do dheasc."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.dolphin.appdata.xml:17
msgid ""
"Dolphin also comes with an integrated terminal that allows you to run "
"commands on the current folder. You can extend the capabilities of Dolphin "
"even further with powerful plugins to adapt it to your workflow. You can use "
"the git integration plugin to interact with git repositories, or the "
"Nextcloud plugin to synchronize your files online, and much more."
msgstr ""
"Tagann críochfort comhtháite le Dolphin freisin a ligeann duit orduithe a "
"rith ar an bhfillteán reatha. Is féidir leat cumais Dolphin a leathnú níos "
"faide fós le breiseáin chumhachtacha chun é a oiriúnú do do shreabhadh "
"oibre. Is féidir leat an breiseán comhtháthaithe git a úsáid chun "
"idirghníomhú le stórtha git, nó an breiseán Nextcloud chun do chuid comhad a "
"shioncrónú ar líne, agus i bhfad níos mó."

